                           Easy Menu Changelog

1.0.3 - 2008/10/12
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Bugfix: the 'Options...' item was not hidden when the relative
   preference was unchecked. Only the menu separator was correctly hidden
=========================================================================

1.0.2 - 2008/10/11
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Bugfix of a misleading error message when checking available and
   required icons (thanks to JaiBee)
 - Improved the required and available icons checks for logo icon and
   mailing list sub-menu icons
=========================================================================

1.0.1 - 2008/10/05
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Bugfix of an encoding problem for DTD generated files. (LP: #278085)
=========================================================================

1.0.0 - 2008/09/24
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Improvements on the XSD validation for single and multiline strings.
 - Removal of some validation checks done in the code that now are done
   directly in the XSD validation process. (the transition from DTD
   validation to XSD validation was suggested by Aldo Armiento)
 - Internal transition in the management of the custom pages from
   dictionaries (unordered) to list of tuples (ordered). (LP: #263674)
 - Extension's ID can now be email address strings as well as UUID for
   a full compatibility with the Mozilla Developer Center documentation.
   (as suggested by JaiBee).
 - Better and more rigorous email address validation check
 - Bugfix various
=========================================================================

1.0rc1 - 2008/08/27
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Added the possibility to set an icon for the 'mailmenu' tags
 - Improvement of regular expressions that provide some additional
   validation of the XML input
 - Added feature: the specification of the tooltiptext in every allowed
   item and menu is made feasible (as suggested by Meisok).
 - Review of the Doc string of some functions
 - Changed the comment character in the '.properties' files
 - Transition from the external xml.dom library to the xml.etree
   ElementTree standard library for the whole project.
 - Transition from the external xml.parsers.xmlproc library to the lxml
   external library for the DTD input validation.
   (The only external requirement is now lxml instead of PyXml)
 - Transition from the DTD validation to the XMLSchema (XSD) validation
 - Simplified some checks on the XML input that now are already checked
   by the XSD validation
 - Simplified parsing of background and border colors on menus using a
   common function
 - Changed the preamble of extension's files
 - Added feature: the '--test' ('-t') command line option was added to
   allow to only check the validity of the XML input without any file
   generation (as suggested by Andrea Corbellini).
=========================================================================

1.0beta3 - 2008/08/08
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Bugfix of an encoding issue in the .dtd and .properties files
 - Bugfix in the example XML file
 - Removed full stop at the end of error lines output
 - Changed the quoting in the whole project, now single quote is used
 - Optimization of some code related to the extension logo
 - Added a try-except that was left commented
 - Modified the import lines according to PEP 8 Style Guide
=========================================================================

1.0beta2 - 2008/07/14
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - Added this Changelog
 - Better parameters management according to the Andrea Corbellini
   suggestion
 - Optimization of the 'setCompatibilityMaxVersion' function
 - Bugfix of an issue in the 'compatibility' option
 - Bugfix of localized files building process
 - Change of the text printed with the --version option
 - Merge of Andrea Corbellini 2008/07/09 merge proposal
=========================================================================

1.0beta - 2008/07/07
-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 - First public release
=========================================================================
